E.F. Hutton said it named Steven Peras, formerly vice president in charge of all spot tradingfor Irving Bank's &lt;V> Irving Trust Co, senior vice presidentfor worldwide foreign exchange trading.    Peras, 30, will direct Hutton's foreign corporate andindividual foreign exchange account development, andmarket-making in currencies for the firm on a worldwide basis,Hutton said. Hutton has foreign exchange trading operations inLondon and New York. Reuter&#3;